{
  "stem": "17299.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A certain amount did, a certain amount did not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some in the public offices changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were open feelings of anti-Semitism against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had-- when you went in, you had to wait to talk to them, or they would treat you like dirt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not till '35.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, you could not go in a restaurant anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Say in a bar or something, you were insulted and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That started after '35 after the Nuremberg Laws went into effect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, I had some sense I was going out with, a Gentile, and I got told not to go anymore because he had sisters, and it would be a question if I will go out with a girl or with a boy.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some Jews welcomed the Nuremberg Laws because there was a lot of intermarriage going on in Germany, and they said it's good.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It will stop the intermarriages in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found out we were second class citizens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We wanted to leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father did not want to leave Germany because the business was still good, and he was a soldier in the First World War with seven of his brothers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were eight brothers who were soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two were killed on the War, and he was 100% German first and Jew second.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we saw what was going on, we wanted to get out of Germany, and we started rebelling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My twin brother was the first one to rebel, and he left Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He joined the Foreign Legion, then became a French citizen afterwards because we had relatives in France who made the arrangement when he stayed in the French army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he got killed in May, 1945, fighting against the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
